    "description": "准备好参加我们的找对子拼图游戏吧! 你会喜欢它帮助提高你的记忆力和注意力的能力。无论你是一个孩子还是一个大胡子，这个游戏都会让你在短时间内微笑和思考!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/2062bf97a2c1ef426bb0acd48f935bb6.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> 。<br><br>要玩这个游戏，只需点击邮票，将其翻转过来。试着找到一对匹配的邮票。如果你没有找到，不要担心--邮票会重新翻转过来。你完成每一关的速度越快，动作越少，你的最终得分就越高<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.poster.avif?t=1742541234\" width=618 height=124 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.webm?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2217440/extras/4556b676df7416a9599c81dafc0ff92a.mp4?t=1742541234\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br><br>邀请你的朋友和你一起玩，看看谁能得到最高分。谁知道呢，你可能会成为记忆力和注意力的冠军!",
